{"type": "article", "id": 29068, "title": "蒲公英天气装置", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-04T05:10:58Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607040249170HSYroXedCtfciDF.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">空中飘扬的蒲公英通常是春天来临的信号，然而我们现在很少有机会直观地感受到气候变化，往往都是通过或大或小的屏幕了解天气信息，JungHoon Lee 为此设计了一款以蒲公英为灵感的天气装置 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/38823793/WEATHER-OR-NOT\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dandelion</a>，让人们可以用手感受到室外的风力与温度。它通过无线网络与智能设备相连以读取天气的相关数据，随后将他们转化为通过触觉感知的互动信息。Dandelion 内置了制冷/热模块和一个小风扇，当你用手触碰装置时，风扇会模拟风力以及温度让孢子摇晃，气氛灯也会根据温度点亮。虽然它不能提供精准的数字，但通过这种方式换新衣橱也是个有意思的选择。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704024951jVd9v3QzP6Meic8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704025017h5DBuzGpcbjFVSsE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607040250362CYbxFK9XSlmQsIh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704025053ernJylN2KcTjXI9o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}